  "content": "<p data-pid=\"2gIyl2oG\">本系列专门介绍 SuperMemo 的各种小技巧和绕坑方法。</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/797904700\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">SuperMemo tips</a><p data-pid=\"xmqyriCZ\">如果直接打开 sm18.exe，效果很可能是这样的：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-3fd9ed0d06482c525591afb692d9fda8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1766\" data-rawheight=\"1250\" data-original-token=\"v2-3fd9ed0d06482c525591afb692d9fda8\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4faa96a86b657ac2a8992277657a6d1a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1766\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3fd9ed0d06482c525591afb692d9fda8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1766&#39; height=&#39;1250&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1766\" data-rawheight=\"1250\" data-original-token=\"v2-3fd9ed0d06482c525591afb692d9fda8\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4faa96a86b657ac2a8992277657a6d1a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1766\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3fd9ed0d06482c525591afb692d9fda8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-3fd9ed0d06482c525591afb692d9fda8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"ch5BJaJV\">解决方法如下：</p><p data-pid=\"09ySnQz2\">右键 sm18.exe，点击属性</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-781831f4d2891cf5cdbce275fb97d0ae_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"856\" data-rawheight=\"1112\" data-original-token=\"v2-781831f4d2891cf5cdbce275fb97d0ae\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4e3a767af266f86b43efb023343a63ae_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"856\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-781831f4d2891cf5cdbce275fb97d0ae_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;856&#39; height=&#39;1112&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"856\" data-rawheight=\"1112\" data-original-token=\"v2-781831f4d2891cf5cdbce275fb97d0ae\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4e3a767af266f86b43efb023343a63ae_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"856\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-781831f4d2891cf5cdbce275fb97d0ae_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-781831f4d2891cf5cdbce275fb97d0ae_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"_5kb0nre\">进入兼容性设置，点击更改高 DPI 设置</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-00b6a967c0bcedb0983402a99e8bc959_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"864\" data-rawheight=\"1270\" data-original-token=\"v2-00b6a967c0bcedb0983402a99e8bc959\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-02cdf8986860d9493300b67a5f070d0f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"864\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-00b6a967c0bcedb0983402a99e8bc959_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;864&#39; height=&#39;1270&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"864\" data-rawheight=\"1270\" data-original-token=\"v2-00b6a967c0bcedb0983402a99e8bc959\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-02cdf8986860d9493300b67a5f070d0f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"864\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-00b6a967c0bcedb0983402a99e8bc959_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-00b6a967c0bcedb0983402a99e8bc959_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"28x3KYmU\">勾选替代高 DPI 缩放行为，选择系统增强，确定保存</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-760130b9251eb1afbf8bd6667cb4ea32_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"808\" data-rawheight=\"950\" data-original-token=\"v2-760130b9251eb1afbf8bd6667cb4ea32\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-764f903fb10032a689225ed1494bf043_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"808\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-760130b9251eb1afbf8bd6667cb4ea32_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;808&#39; height=&#39;950&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"808\" data-rawheight=\"950\" data-original-token=\"v2-760130b9251eb1afbf8bd6667cb4ea32\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-764f903fb10032a689225ed1494bf043_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"808\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-760130b9251eb1afbf8bd6667cb4ea32_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-760130b9251eb1afbf8bd6667cb4ea32_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8QzWgDNX\">最终效果：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f1e5eecbc3e64adf48a12131bc5921f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1762\" data-rawheight=\"1250\" data-original-token=\"v2-0f1e5eecbc3e64adf48a12131bc5921f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-efef95af9c8a8f2dc8872994201bf0dd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1762\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0f1